臂有骨折、手腕脫臼，需要進行手術，以鈦金屬固定骨折的位置。"},{"pid":"ebcfa5824d185e7dc0268970a67b6db21618db48","tid":2147481,"uid":183090,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:42:17.000Z","msg":"去左北京做質子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭做唔晒所有阿爺比嘅功課都唔駛諗住贖返個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44ccd41b0ecf75e36a60a345079373f6c0518c7","tid":2147481,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:43:17.000Z","msg":"Who cares"},{"pid":"5bbee9186df37a521d0d1f57c1553516b63cf29f","tid":2147481,"uid":282359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0e72e0c01d6a076f7e6b884f6d26d718a0064f2b","tid":2147481,"uid":292343,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:22:13.000Z","msg":"如果比我估中，北京應該早收咗幾日風。<br />\n<br />\n驚班港共垃圾跳船"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T09:45:18.000Z","msg":"似了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支支都知班賤種靠唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"044ba19fa078c253cabae992b79a8a03fd8cb033","tid":2147481,"uid":292343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T10:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef620e360a98e2f1d75c2346f5a6db289bd635e6","tid":2147481,"uid":260744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T10:39:18.000Z","msg":"食緊水餃， 巧巧味"},{"pid":"e1e80991ee75528aa948368f22ab7c01e028e8ed","tid":2147481,"uid":292343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef620e360a98e2f1d75c2346f5a6db289bd635e6","tid":2147481,"uid":260744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T10:39:18.000Z","msg":"食緊水餃， 巧巧味"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\"